{
  "text": "Of the three things you mentioned that we could do for the instrument's benefit, would you clarify the last one? I didn't quite understand that. I am Ra. As the entity which you are allows its being to empathize with another being, so then it may choose to share with the other-self those energies which may be salubrious to the other-self. The mechanism of these energy transfers is the thought or, more precisely, the thought-form for any thought is a form or symbol or thing that is an object seen in time/space reference.",
